{
  "stem": "7684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were Jewish, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember much about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know-- I don't want to remember, all these years, what happened in that time, I think.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's the reason-- eh, perhaps I felt too dumb, or-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just blocked it out perhaps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There are some parts that I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That the man told me, one day, that I can go and visit the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a Jewish family hidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was so happy to go and talk with a Jewish family and go there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So these people upstairs were not long there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow I had no connections with them-- somehow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to this Jewish family-- Next door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next door.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a-- every Jew in Holland had a passport with J in that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I went next door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was happy to see some Jewish people, just ordinary people like I was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the minute that I came in, the police came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Dutch police.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what has now happened-- the people where I was hidden, they were traitors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because after me, 20-- I found out after the war, 28 Jews were caught there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when Jews were hidden by non-Jews, the non-Jewish people were punished, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were also sent to concentration camp, mostly only the men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And none of this happened to these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I came in there, into the house from this family-- that was the lawyer's family that took in this whole family-- they say-- and I say to them, oh, I'm a nurse, I come to help these people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they say, do you have your passport?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
